<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>水瓶座 on Lucky Stone</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/tags/%E6%B0%B4%E7%93%B6%E5%BA%A7/</link><description>Recent content in 水瓶座 on Lucky Stone</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://luckystonetw.com/tags/%E6%B0%B4%E7%93%B6%E5%BA%A7/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>風象星座能量解析：雙子天秤水瓶的風之性格與守護水晶</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E9%A2%A8%E8%B1%A1%E6%98%9F%E5%BA%A7%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E9%9B%99%E5%AD%90%E5%A4%A9%E7%A7%A4%E6%B0%B4%E7%93%B6%E7%9A%84%E9%A2%A8%E4%B9%8B%E6%80%A7%E6%A0%BC%E8%88%87%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6/</link><pubDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E9%A2%A8%E8%B1%A1%E6%98%9F%E5%BA%A7%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E9%9B%99%E5%AD%90%E5%A4%A9%E7%A7%A4%E6%B0%B4%E7%93%B6%E7%9A%84%E9%A2%A8%E4%B9%8B%E6%80%A7%E6%A0%BC%E8%88%87%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;風有很多種吹拂的方式——有的是春天的穿堂風，在每扇窗之間穿梭，帶來各個房間的消息；有的是傍晚的微風，溫柔地拂過水面，讓一切歸於和諧的漣漪；有的是高空的氣流，看不見摸不著，卻悄悄改變了整片天空的走向。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>紫水晶星座配對：雙魚、水瓶、射手為什麼特別有緣？</title><link>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E6%98%9F%E5%BA%A7%E9%85%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%9B%99%E9%AD%9A%E6%B0%B4%E7%93%B6%E5%B0%84%E6%89%8B%E7%82%BA%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%A3/</link><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://luckystonetw.com/post/%E7%B4%AB%E6%B0%B4%E6%99%B6%E6%98%9F%E5%BA%A7%E9%85%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%9B%99%E9%AD%9A%E6%B0%B4%E7%93%B6%E5%B0%84%E6%89%8B%E7%82%BA%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%A3/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;同樣一顆紫水晶，有人戴了感覺渾身舒暢，有人帶了幾個月幾乎沒感覺。這不全然是「信不信的問題」——星座跟水晶的共振確實有差。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>